songs.title: Coming Back Home for Good
songs.lyrics:
If you think I'm leaving
If you feel I could
Well think it over baby
I'm coming back home for good

Did it wrong, misunderstood
Taking care of you was all I should

Whenever you think it's over now
Whenever you see me down and out
Forget about it baby
You and me is what it's all about

Tried to run, thought I could
Now I'm coming back home for good

If you think I'm leaving
If you feel I'm gone
Well think it over baby
I'm coming back home for good

Did it wrong, misunderstood
Now I'm coming back home for good

Tried to run, thought I could
Now I'm coming back home for good
